# Customer Insights and Pain Points

**What our research revealed**

| Customer Segment | Primary Pain Point | Impact Score | Opportunity Size |
|------------------|-------------------|--------------|------------------|
| **Large Enterprises** | Complex integrations | 9/10 | $800M |
| **Growing Companies** | Scalability limitations | 8/10 | $650M |
| **Remote Teams** | Communication gaps | 8/10 | $550M |
| **Project Managers** | Workflow visibility | 7/10 | $400M |
| **IT Administrators** | Security compliance | 9/10 | $300M |

::: warning
**Critical Gap:** 67% of customers struggle with cross-platform data synchronization
:::

@notes:
- Customer research drives feature priorities
- Enterprise integration biggest opportunity
- Remote work trends create new requirements
- Security compliance increasingly important

