# Q1 2025: Foundation and Integration

**Building the platform for future growth**

::: info
**Q1 Major Releases:**
- **Universal API Gateway** - Unified integration platform
- **Mobile App 3.0** - Complete redesign for mobile-first experience
- **Advanced Analytics Dashboard** - Real-time insights and reporting
- **Security Framework Upgrade** - SOC 2 Type II compliance
:::

**Timeline:** January - March 2025

| Feature | Development | Testing | Release |
|---------|-------------|---------|---------|
| API Gateway | Jan 15 | Feb 15 | Mar 1 |
| Mobile App | Jan 1 | Feb 20 | Mar 15 |
| Analytics | Feb 1 | Mar 1 | Mar 20 |
| Security | Jan 10 | Feb 25 | Mar 10 |

@notes:
- Q1 focuses on platform stability and enterprise features
- API gateway enables all future integrations
- Mobile redesign addresses user experience gaps
- Security compliance opens enterprise market

