# Technology Stack Evolution

**Modernizing our development platform**

::: info
**2025 Technology Initiatives:**
- **Microservices Migration** - Decompose monolithic architecture
- **Cloud-Native Infrastructure** - Kubernetes deployment
- **Modern Frontend Framework** - React 18 with Next.js
- **Event-Driven Architecture** - Apache Kafka implementation
- **Observability Platform** - Comprehensive monitoring and logging
:::

**Technical debt reduction: 20% of engineering capacity**

@notes:
- Technology modernization enables feature velocity
- Microservices improve scalability and reliability
- Cloud-native reduces operational overhead
- Event-driven architecture supports real-time features

